review_blob: Keg at Amersham beer shop, Amersham, Bucks. A black coloured pour with a healthy beige head on top. Roasty, malty, coffee aroma. Tastes the same, roasty, malty, coffee, some chocolate. Quite elegant and complex, very nice indeed.
